name: Bumblebee Outfit
description:
High quality ladies balck and yellow Bumble Bee fancy dress costume to fit UK size 10-14. Includes: Dress, Headpiece, Wings, Gloves and Black Stockings

Wanting a theme thats different but still looks hot? Try these Bumble Bee Outfits on for size, youll be in for one buzzing time!

name: Hen Party Memento Book
description:
Pink memento book with empty frame on the front cover. The book contains approx 12 blank pages and it measures approx 21cm x 15cm.

Can't think of any peresnt ideas for the special lady on her hen do? These memento books are guarenteed to put a smile on the Bride-To-Be's face. Get everyone on the hen do to sign the book before presenting the gift and pop a nice photo of her in the front cover. Add anything you like from the hen party into it afterwards!

name: Pack of 6 Hen Party Flags
description:
Black and Pink 'Girls on Tour' flags, with a black pole and a gold top. 
Flag size 15.5cm x 10.5cm and Pole size 28cm.

Need to let everyone in the town know that your hen party have arrived and are out and about? These flags are perfect for catching attention and a fun accessory for you and the lovely ladies on your crazy night out.

name: Pink Shot Glass Necklace Accessory
description:
Plastic Pink "Warning - Hen Party' tinted shot glass , with a 84cm long beaded pink chain.

Need to encourage the ladies to drink on the big night out? One of these fun accessories each for the girls to hang around their neck and play drinking games with is perfect to get everyone in the mood!

name: School Girl Costume Set
description:
A 4 peice school girl set including a red tartan skirt, with black consealed zip, white cropped stretchy shirt with matching red tartan trim, matching red tartan tie and red ribbon hairclip

Trying to find the perfect naughty school girl look to make the girls look extra hot on your hen doo? Look no further, as this set contains everything you will need to acomplish this and more
